{% schema %}
  {
    
    "name": "Section 6",
    "tag": "section",
    "class": "gps-628176815433122403 gps gpsil",
    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/yet74e-p1/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=628176815231337059&sectionId=628176815433122403)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggcfGlqPD0m_text","label":"ggcfGlqPD0m_text","default":"<span style=\"background-color:rgba(249,207,207,0);\">In to ni „samo starost\"&nbsp;</span><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(249,207,207,0);\">— to je artritis.</span>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg6YXa6aMMp_text","label":"gg6YXa6aMMp_text","default":"<p>&nbsp;Artritis ni ena sama stvar. Sklep napade na treh ravneh hkrati:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggSP4akumnZ_text","label":"ggSP4akumnZ_text","default":"1. Vnetje"},{"type":"html","id":"ggirUpICCfz_text","label":"ggirUpICCfz_text","default":"<p>&nbsp;Ob obremenitvi in staranju se v sklepu sproži vnetni odziv. Povzroča oteklino, togost in bolečino ter pospešuje razgradnjo sklepnega tkiva.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxJHSujBHe_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggxJHSujBHe_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0970/1284/2821/files/close-up-cute-their-greyhound-dog.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxJHSujBHe_srcSet_mobile_src","label":"ggxJHSujBHe_srcSet_mobile_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0970/1284/2821/files/hf_20260713_165343_fa82d984-8de5-433f-88d2-3d5047daa731.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gg6L1wIayZ9_text","label":"gg6L1wIayZ9_text","default":"2. Obraba hrustanca"},{"type":"html","id":"ggp4r_K7eyj_text","label":"ggp4r_K7eyj_text","default":"<p>&nbsp;Hrustanec blaži trenje med kostmi. S časom in vnetjem se tanjša, zato se obremenitev vse bolj prenaša neposredno na kost — gibanje postane težje in boleče.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggkRHLaGvcY_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggkRHLaGvcY_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0970/1284/2821/files/labrador-dog-stairs-indoors.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggkRHLaGvcY_srcSet_mobile_src","label":"ggkRHLaGvcY_srcSet_mobile_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0970/1284/2821/files/hf_20260713_165719_3d2d789b-0b91-400e-b9ae-5854d33e0906.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gg9eVMNCN48_text","label":"gg9eVMNCN48_text","default":"3. Oksidativni stres"},{"type":"html","id":"ggl09UBT6OE_text","label":"ggl09UBT6OE_text","default":"<p>Prosti radikali poškodujejo celice hrustanca hitreje, kot jih telo obnavlja. To upočasni regeneracijo in pospeši nadaljnjo obrabo sklepa.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnfCpuhU9a_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggnfCpuhU9a_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0970/1284/2821/files/person-walking-black-white-dog-street.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnfCpuhU9a_srcSet_mobile_src","label":"ggnfCpuhU9a_srcSet_mobile_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0970/1284/2821/files/hf_20260713_165449_031f85b0-57db-4060-8d07-cab73b4ad3bf.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggHVpq8Bw6v_text","label":"ggHVpq8Bw6v_text","default":"<p>Ker vsi trije procesi delujejo hkrati, dodatek, ki naslavlja le enega (npr. glukozamin za hrustanec), ne zadošča — vnetje in oksidativni stres delujeta naprej.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg4qxCpG_WZ_text","label":"gg4qxCpG_WZ_text","default":"Zakaj se artritis pri psih sploh razvije?"},{"type":"html","id":"gg8qsIhlYTR_text","label":"gg8qsIhlYTR_text","default":"<p><strong>1. Staranje</strong><br>Z leti se presnova upočasni, telo pa hrustanec in sklepno tkivo obnavlja počasneje kot v mladosti. Drobne poškodbe, ki bi jih mlad pes zlahka popravil, se pri starejšem začnejo kopičiti.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>2. Teža in velikost</strong><br>Vsak korak pomeni obremenitev sklepa. Večji in težji ko je pes, večji je pritisk na hrustanec — zato se pri velikih pasmah in pri psih s prekomerno težo sklepi praviloma obrabijo prej.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>3. Vsakodnevna obremenitev</strong><br>Skoki na kavč in v avto, tek, igra, stopnice … leta ponavljajočega se gibanja postopoma tanjšajo hrustanec. To je povsem normalno — a se sčasoma sešteje.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>4. Pasma in genetika</strong><br>Nekatere pasme so k težavam s sklepi nagnjene že po naravi, bodisi zaradi zgradbe sklepov bodisi zaradi hitre rasti v mladosti. Pri njih se prvi znaki lahko pojavijo prej kot pri drugih.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><br>Teh dejavnikov ne moreš povsem odpraviti. Lahko pa sklepom daš podporo, ki obrabo upočasni in psu pomaga ostati gibčen dlje. In prav zato je pomembno, s čim to podporo daš.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg4eGQgaWCO_text","label":"gg4eGQgaWCO_text","default":"Zato smo razvili naravno rešitev <span style=\"background-color:rgba(248,170,167,0.77);\">MobiMix</span><span style=\"background-color:rgba(255,255,255,0);\">&nbsp;</span>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_9Z4Xi7Dn_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg_9Z4Xi7Dn_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0970/1284/2821/files/Kaching-Bundles-1x_MobiMix_-_no_bg_430x_381557d8-6e6e-48b9-a785-7a9f2050343f.webp"},{"type":"html","id":"gg6y9J6PrDJ_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg6y9J6PrDJ_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0970/1284/2821/files/unnamed_1.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggJVm_ClUUO_text","label":"ggJVm_ClUUO_text","default":"<p>Blaž Petelinek Ledinski dr. vet. med.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggbP__mjgNf_text","label":"ggbP__mjgNf_text","default":"<p>“MobiMix je formuliran z 8 klinično preverjenimi sestavinami. Pomaga vašemu psu ostati aktiven in brez bolečin z podporo <strong>obnovi hrustanca</strong>, <strong>mazanju sklepov</strong> in <strong>zmanjšanju vnetja</strong>.”</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggdr0XuDD2-_text","label":"ggdr0XuDD2-_text","default":"<strong>Priporočen s strani veterinarjev&nbsp;</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg86EGLjw_k_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg86EGLjw_k_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/5214/2562/files/gempages_518090459516502570-fd204759-bd9d-4564-9e30-3ff2facb72de.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggG0H5adSVb_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggG0H5adSVb_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/5214/2562/files/gempages_518090459516502570-83e1af8d-ad67-4b33-83ee-51f80fee6167.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gg9GlPLSl85_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg9GlPLSl85_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/5214/2562/files/gempages_518090459516502570-eee8f948-1544-47ee-acc0-8fe5b99f735a.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggh1s894EeZ_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggh1s894EeZ_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/5214/2562/files/gempages_518090459516502570-2b1f58d6-457d-4734-a2f5-b5db983ef2fb.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggCGpXbTO3t_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggCGpXbTO3t_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/5214/2562/files/gempages_518090459516502570-af77021a-12c9-40dd-8132-2c59edf287dc.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gg4yvV7IvVk_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg4yvV7IvVk_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/5214/2562/files/gempages_518090459516502570-af77021a-12c9-40dd-8132-2c59edf287dc.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggCYAcXPLwU_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggCYAcXPLwU_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/5214/2562/files/gempages_518090459516502570-af77021a-12c9-40dd-8132-2c59edf287dc.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggdzuoRTv4E_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggdzuoRTv4E_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/5214/2562/files/gempages_518090459516502570-af77021a-12c9-40dd-8132-2c59edf287dc.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggVXRdm9x4u_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggVXRdm9x4u_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/